* &quot;Who Goes There!&quot; (1952) – Alex Cornwall
* &quot;Meet Me Tonight&quot; (1952) – Stella Cartwright (segment &quot;Ways and Means&quot;)
* &quot;The Voice of Merrill&quot; (1952) – Alycia
* &quot;Background&quot; (1953) – Barbie Lomax
* &quot;Knave of Hearts&quot; (1954) – Catherine Ripois
