=== Personnel ===
* Gato Barbieri – tenor saxophone, flute, vocal
* Franco D&#x27;Andrea – piano
* Franco Goldani, Wolmer Beltrani – accordion
* Jean-François Jenny-Clark, Giovanni Tommaso – bass
* Pierino Munari – drums
